          Commercial Incentives & Tax Benefits
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Maximize your ROI with available programs and accelerated depreciation
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-blue-100 rounded-xl p-8 border-2 border-blue-200">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Accelerated Depreciation</h3>
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-600 text-white text-sm font-semibold rounded-full"
